author: tellison
msg: Fix for HARMONY-802 ([classlib][nio] java.nio.ByteBuffer.compareTo( ByteBuffer) returns wrong value)

author: hindessm
msg: Rather than take what we think we need from classlib JRE, take everything
except what we know we don't want.  This obsoletes my previous commit and
also fixes the security provider issue.  Hopefully it will avoid trivial
changes if/when classlib changes at least until we have a top-level build.
